pageProduct.name: Swisse Beauty Collagen Renew 120g Powder
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Beauty Collagen Renew Powder is a premium quality beauty supplement featuring Collagen Peptides, Vitamin C and Ashwagandha. This great tasting formula helps improve skin elasticity and firmness, support skin regeneration and help the body adapt to the effects of stress.

Helps support collagen formation, skin repair and skin elasticity
Helps support  the body adapt to the effects of stress
Great tasting natural berry flavour
Quick dissolving formula that's 97.3%  sugar free

Size: 120g

Warnings

If symptoms persist, consult your healthcare practitioner talk to your health professional. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If you are pregnant, or considering becoming pregnant, do not take without consulting a health professional.

Ingredients

COLLAGEN (Hydrolysed collagen) 2.5 g
VITAMIN C (ascorbic acid) 50 mg
ASHWAGANDHA (Withania somnifera extract 60 mg) equiv. dry root 3 g

Directions

Using the enclosed scoop, mix one level scoop (6 g) with 250 mL of water or juice. Consume once daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Once dissolved, consume immediately. Some settling of the powder may occur after mixing.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken. Powder may settle prior to opening.
